Description: Standard methods for analysis of mutation data following error-
    corrected sequencing (ECS) for the purpose of mutagencity assessment.
    Functions include importing the mutation lists provided by a variant
    caller, and a set of analytical tools for statistical testing and
    visualization of mutation data; comparison to COSMIC and/or germline
    signatures; etc.
